title: AKH HOUSEWARE Clothes Drying Rack, with Sock Clips, Metal Laundry Rack, Foldable, Space-Saving, Free-Standing Airer, with 2 Height-Adjustable Gullwings, Indoor Outdoor Use
features: All-in-One Drying Solution – Features 24 hanging rods and 27 clips to handle large laundry loads, from heavy towels to delicate socks.
Adjustable Wings – Two upper wings with three height settings (39.4", 44.1", and 49.2") let you dry clothes of various lengths, including shirts, trousers, and linens.
Space-Saving Foldable Design – Folds down to just 2.8"D for compact storage in closets, behind doors, or under beds.
Portable & Lightweight – Easy to carry and reposition around your home, balcony, or garden.
Rust-Resistant Build – Sturdy steel tubes with a corrosion-resistant coating ensure long-lasting use indoors or out.
Heavy-Duty Capacity – Supports up to 55 lb, providing ample strength for heavy garments and wet loads.
Secure Hanging – Comes with 27 clips to keep smaller items like socks and underwear from falling off.
Quick Assembly, No Tools Needed – Assemble effortlessly with numbered parts and clear instructions — no screws or tools required.
Versatile Use – Ideal for air drying clothes, towels, blankets, baby items, or delicates in eco-friendly style.
Reliable and Eco-Conscious – Reduces energy use from dryers while maintaining the shape and quality of your garments.
description: Dry Smarter, Not Harder — with This All-in-One Clothes Drying Rack Say goodbye to limited drying space and tangled clothes with this multifunctional clothes airer. Designed to handle everything from bulky towels to delicate socks, it features 24 robust hanging rods and 27 secure clips — enough room for an entire load of laundry. The adjustable wings offer three height levels (39.4", 44.1", and 49.2"), so whether you're drying long trousers, shirts, or sheets, everything fits just right. Crafted with rust-resistant steel and durable plastic connectors, this rack supports up to 55 lb of laundry, making it perfect for daily family use. When not in use, simply fold it flat to a compact 2.8 inches deep for easy storage in tight spaces. Lightweight and easy to move, it's perfect for use in the home, on balconies, or even outdoors. Best of all, no tools are needed for assembly — just follow the step-by-step guide and you'll be drying in no time. Whether you're cutting down on energy bills or preserving your clothes’ quality, this drying rack is the eco-friendly essential every home needs.
